  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Furion W402 WashBeam is a versatile, IP65-rated moving head light fixture that excels in both beam and wash applications. Equipped with 7 x 45 W RGBW flat-field LEDs and a motorized zoom that enables seamless transitions between a narrow 3.1deg beam and a wide 36.6deg wash, it adapts easily to any quest. Grand concerts, theatrical productions, live events and more are all within its realm. Precise, customizable color temperatures come from its intelligent white mode with user calibrated 7500 K output and the CTC channel that offers stepless white light between 2700 K and 7500 K. The fixture’s 16-bit dimming capabilities deliver smooth, calibrated dimming effects, enhancing the quality of lighting transitions. For environments requiring minimal noise, the studio mode offers whisper-quiet fan operation ensuring discreet performance. Adjustable PWM frequencies guarantee uncompromised quality in filming situations too. Comprehensive control options include basic, advanced and customized DMX modes, CRMX, W-DMX, Art-Net, sACN and RDM. Power Pro True inputs and outputs add power-linking possibilities. Its housing, forged from magnesium and aluminum, is both sturdy and lightweight, ensuring durability and minimal maintenance. The IP65 rating guarantees that the fixture is dust-tight and protected against water, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use. The Furion W402 WashBeam is a premium lighting solution that combines versatility with superior performance. Its rugged build, seamless movements and advanced zoom and dimming features make it a veritable powerhouse.",
